Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.42,0:00:13.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.12,0:00:16.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祭典的時候沒給你們
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.98,0:00:18.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然有點不合季節
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.39,0:00:21.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很棒啊  海外旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.66,0:00:23.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.32,0:00:25.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小時候我們也去過
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.72,0:00:26.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.69,0:00:28.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐完全想不起來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.58,0:00:30.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.74,0:00:32.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一說…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.12,0:00:39.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像吃過附有冰淇淋的大薄餅和擠滿奶油的香蕉派…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.20,0:00:41.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就只記得這些啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.13,0:00:42.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  那就出發吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.27,0:00:42.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.51,0:00:45.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  走吧  走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.72,0:02:25.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  吃飯咯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.77,0:02:28.89,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（吶吶  進軍海外吧！）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.15,0:02:29.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.15,0:02:35.15,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}番外篇　　計劃 !
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.12,0:02:42.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓  這邊  這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.61,0:02:44.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給  梓喵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.32,0:02:46.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經幫你點了香蕉奶昔哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.58,0:02:47.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.17,0:02:49.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曬黑的皮膚已經恢復了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.86,0:02:51.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年輕嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.35,0:02:53.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新陳代謝簡直跟嬰兒差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.91,0:02:55.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那有點年輕過頭了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.72,0:02:57.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小梓  這是給你的禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.16,0:03:02.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇～謝謝紬學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.62,0:03:04.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.10,0:03:06.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓喵的也不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.52,0:03:10.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  對了  剛才的簡訊是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.50,0:03:13.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我們正商量著要去旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.60,0:03:14.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旅行？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.41,0:03:17.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是去海邊  而是要去海外啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.69,0:03:19.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才說「進軍海外」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.50,0:03:22.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過才剛去過夏日節啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.27,0:03:25.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家還是應考生吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.24,0:03:27.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以考完才去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.62,0:03:29.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  畢業旅行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.64,0:03:31.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓喵也一起去嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.17,0:03:34.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起玩會更開心的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.75,0:03:36.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  總之先走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.67,0:03:37.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.78,0:03:43.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有好多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.81,0:03:46.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看指南手冊  然後再商量下去哪兒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.74,0:03:49.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這樣真的沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.63,0:03:52.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏季講習不是快開始了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.33,0:03:56.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然夏季講習和考試複習兩手都會抓
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.31,0:03:59.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過你看  人就是要有零食才會有幹勁嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.49,0:04:01.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,努力過後總得吃點零食啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.93,0:04:06.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是結束後有份期待的話  考試也就能熬過去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.62,0:04:10.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了  你們只是想稍微逃避一下現實吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.87,0:04:12.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒逃啊  才沒逃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.15,0:04:13.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天早上我還好好用功了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.86,0:04:18.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也好  稍微想一下開心的事也好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.08,0:04:21.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連澪學姐也這樣  感覺壓力不小啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.85,0:04:24.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底去哪兒好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.43,0:04:26.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼多真不好選
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.86,0:04:28.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之  只是計劃一下的話… 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.09,0:04:37.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紐約…不錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.42,0:04:38.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,入浴？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.42,0:04:40.52,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（「紐約」=ニューヨーク，「入浴」=ニュウヨク，日語發音相近）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.38,0:04:40.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯小姐  這呆裝得真不怎麼樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.61,0:04:41.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒啦沒啦沒啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.42,0:04:47.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紐約是在美國吧  也就是吉太出生的國家咯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.83,0:04:50.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉太  這是你的家鄉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.61,0:04:52.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉太可能會很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.97,0:04:54.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是回老家…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.83,0:04:57.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澪學姐認為去哪裡好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.15,0:04:58.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我選英國
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.63,0:05:01.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  有種搖滾發源地的感覺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.00,0:05:05.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  去看看演唱會  音樂劇什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.34,0:05:08.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,英國也是紅茶的發源地啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.07,0:05:10.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  到海外去喝茶也不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.65,0:05:14.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「英國」很像「蟋蟀」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.65,0:05:14.79,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（「英國」=イギリス，「蟋蟀」=キリギリス）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.87,0:05:15.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.05,0:05:17.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就別來吐槽了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.90,0:05:19.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼律認為哪裡好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.51,0:05:22.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…夏威夷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.79,0:05:26.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次到國外果然還是去夏威夷比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.29,0:05:28.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小律選得也不怎麼樣嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.99,0:05:31.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天熱的地方冰淇淋會特別好吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.37,0:05:32.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏威夷也不錯嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.93,0:05:34.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…紬學姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.85,0:05:37.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要大家一起的話我去哪裡都行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.71,0:05:38.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好淡定
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.31,0:05:43.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是  只要零食好吃的地方去哪裡都行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.25,0:05:44.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你個貪吃鬼…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.41,0:05:47.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺大家意見完全不統一啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.70,0:05:49.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去我家別墅其實也可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.71,0:05:50.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芬蘭嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.95,0:05:53.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也不錯啊  好想看看極光
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.86,0:05:58.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來  芬蘭有「空氣吉他大賽」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.21,0:05:59.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  吉他
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.98,0:06:03.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要跟吉太一起登場
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.17,0:06:05.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是空氣吉他  所以用不著吉太
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.72,0:06:08.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.76,0:06:11.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦  也沒必要急著決定
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.96,0:06:14.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之  各自再想下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.72,0:06:19.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海外旅行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.15,0:06:22.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.25,0:06:24.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  是小梓啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.03,0:06:26.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去哪兒旅行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.76,0:06:30.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輕音社的大家提到了畢業旅行…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.63,0:06:34.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  我也正計劃著學生會的旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.54,0:06:36.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.01,0:06:41.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是想再去一次京都
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.44,0:06:44.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前有很多想去卻沒去成的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.10,0:06:46.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.69,0:06:48.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輕音社打算去哪裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.68,0:06:50.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都想去海外
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.10,0:06:52.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.68,0:06:57.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摩亨佐·達羅  吳哥窟  馬丘比丘  都想去一次啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.68,0:06:57.73,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}摩亨佐·達羅：又稱死丘，位於巴基斯坦南部的古代印度河流域文明大都會。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.68,0:06:57.73,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}吳哥窟：柬埔寨西北方廟宇，以建築宏偉與浮雕細緻聞名於世，也是世界上最大的廟宇。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.68,0:06:57.73,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}馬丘比丘：位於秘魯境內庫斯科西北的印加遺跡，世界新七大奇跡之一。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.82,0:06:58.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬茲比丘？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.83,0:06:59.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬丘比丘
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.81,0:07:00.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬丘比茲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.26,0:07:04.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…不習慣的話確實挺難念的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.44,0:07:06.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.69,0:07:07.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.51,0:07:12.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺給我留了個面子…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.70,0:07:15.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  憂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.03,0:07:17.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  小梓
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.69,0:07:18.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來買書嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.18,0:07:22.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  稍微給姐姐找點旅行用的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.70,0:07:39.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請進
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.44,0:07:44.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來送麥茶…了…姐姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.38,0:07:46.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  這個？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.24,0:07:49.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不是啊  我剛剛還在好好學習的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.50,0:07:50.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不騙你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.39,0:07:58.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  姐姐你們居然要去海外…我稍微有點擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.08,0:08:00.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.33,0:08:06.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼姐姐  這個給你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.07,0:08:08.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.60,0:08:11.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望姐姐能夠平安歸來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.89,0:08:16.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也繼續計劃海外旅行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.50,0:08:18.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我給小梓發下簡訊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.76,0:08:20.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之先確定目的地吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.83,0:08:26.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此之前還有一件要做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.68,0:08:31.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天在公園集合？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.29,0:08:34.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把錢交出來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.04,0:08:40.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小澪  被抓住的手的拇指向上  使勁揮出手刀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.03,0:08:44.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擺脫後全速逃離
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.63,0:08:48.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  梓
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.06,0:08:51.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事  你們在幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.43,0:08:52.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.30,0:08:54.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,防身術？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.58,0:08:56.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憂給我買的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.80,0:08:58.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果買了這個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.38,0:09:02.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了不浪費小憂的一番好意  大家正在實踐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.31,0:09:04.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓喵也學習一下比較好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.20,0:09:08.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼接下來輪到紬紬和梓喵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.12,0:09:11.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當被人從後面抱住的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.87,0:09:14.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把錢交出來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.96,0:09:17.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不用加上演技吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.25,0:09:19.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得有臨場感的話比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.12,0:09:23.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓喵  用腳後跟踢紬紬的小腿後逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.78,0:09:26.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.39,0:09:28.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受益非淺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.20,0:09:35.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冰～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.26,0:09:39.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來要注意的就是不要迷路了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.47,0:09:41.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看地圖應該就沒問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.27,0:09:44.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話是這麼說  但上次在京都不還是迷路了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.32,0:09:46.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就問路人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.21,0:09:47.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家不會日語哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.57,0:09:49.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紬紬  你會說英語嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.64,0:09:51.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡單的日常對話應該沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.52,0:09:52.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果跟紬走散了怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.55,0:09:55.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那問題就大了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.27,0:09:58.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼從現在開始禁止講日語
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.32,0:09:59.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.18,0:10:03.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之要努力練習到即使不能說英語也能把意思傳達清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.59,0:10:04.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得對
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.83,0:10:07.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK  No日語
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.64,0:10:09.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「日語」本身就是日語吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.80,0:10:11.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK  OK
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.70,0:10:14.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Where very delicious cake shop?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.84,0:10:17.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡有好吃的蛋糕店？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.09,0:10:18.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.62,0:10:20.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種話一般不會問吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.02,0:10:23.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般問的是觀光勝地或能過夜的旅店之類的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.04,0:10:25.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Where my hotel?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.89,0:10:27.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡是我的旅店？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.75,0:10:28.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旅店是你家開的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.57,0:10:31.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然有點怪  但能講出旅店名字的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.81,0:10:33.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家就能幫我們指路了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.53,0:10:36.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「旅店」的英語也是Hotel吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.25,0:10:38.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發音互通嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.73,0:10:42.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像按日語發音說「Wa—ter— please」對方未必能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.45,0:10:43.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,印象中英語課上這麼說過…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.77,0:10:45.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那該怎麼講才行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.47,0:10:48.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是不要拉長  說「Water please」的話比較接近
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.36,0:10:52.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有水人會死哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.47,0:10:56.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起說得半桶水的話  用肢體語言的話可能更好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.51,0:11:02.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也看不出是需要水啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.45,0:11:04.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是個痛苦的人？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.39,0:11:08.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盂蘭盆舞？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.30,0:11:10.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  下雨
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.76,0:11:15.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然也是水  但形容「需要水」是不是太抽象了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.51,0:11:23.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這是祈雨吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.10,0:11:27.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.90,0:11:29.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琴？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.20,0:11:32.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…不是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.20,0:11:36.16,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（「琴」與「事情」同音，所以唯表達的是「沒什麼好笑的」(笑いことじゃない)）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.20,0:11:36.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她說小梓答對了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.48,0:11:39.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然答對了  但這也沒什麼意義啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.32,0:11:42.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且「琴」的意思外國人也不會懂…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.32,0:11:47.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…感覺跟旅行扯得太遠了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.45,0:11:51.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  話說回來大家都有護照嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.94,0:11:52.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.27,0:11:59.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,K-ON!！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.46,0:12:06.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個不能用了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.46,0:12:08.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  過期了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.11,0:12:11.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  反正大家都要去辦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.45,0:12:14.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要的東西有身份證和戶口本
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.27,0:12:17.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有護照用照片和護照申請書
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.27,0:12:19.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有  未成年需要家長的同意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.11,0:12:22.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及身份證明
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.35,0:12:25.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有手續費
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.52,0:12:27.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要這麼多東西？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.44,0:12:29.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會幫姐姐準備齊全的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.40,0:12:34.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出國可真麻煩啊  憂…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.06,0:12:39.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記得應該有申請夏季講習時候用過的照片…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.40,0:12:43.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  辦護照穿校服的話有點…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.03,0:12:48.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身份證明…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.13,0:12:52.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那學生手冊應該就可以了吧  裡面有學生證
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.20,0:12:56.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼後天  把需要的東西湊齊然後集合
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.26,0:12:59.26,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（發送中）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.26,0:13:00.64,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（已發出）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.88,0:13:05.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還沒決定要出國
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.05,0:13:08.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和和也去辦一個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.26,0:13:09.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等決定了再說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.57,0:13:11.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  小佐和
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.16,0:13:14.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.70,0:13:15.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.83,0:13:17.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小佐和也是來辦護照的？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.68,0:13:21.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼護照啊  我是來拍健身中心入會照片的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.16,0:13:23.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,健身中心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.83,0:13:25.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小佐和你要入會啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.08,0:13:27.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你往哪兒看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.32,0:13:30.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還假裝個什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.50,0:13:33.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個煩惱多多的年紀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.90,0:13:34.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您掉東西了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.06,0:13:35.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.94,0:13:36.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.33,0:13:38.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小佐和  好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.12,0:13:41.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺稍微有點緊張…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.19,0:13:44.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再照一次吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.11,0:13:46.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也要照啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.29,0:13:49.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來  你們說護照…要去海外嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.84,0:13:50.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.90,0:13:52.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？去哪兒？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.66,0:13:54.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今未定
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.06,0:13:55.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.86,0:14:01.70,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}彩色證件照  立等可取！！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.86,0:14:01.70,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}出像清晰  重複拍照  護照專用
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.86,0:14:01.70,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}另有親切的語音嚮導功能
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.05,0:13:58.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她們好像計劃著畢業旅行時候去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.49,0:14:01.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前先制定好應考複習計劃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.91,0:14:04.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小佐和沒去過海外嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.87,0:14:06.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然有  還是學生的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.91,0:14:08.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去過哪兒？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.41,0:14:11.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沖繩？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.57,0:14:12.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.46,0:14:14.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師  沖繩不算海外…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.70,0:14:17.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道  撐撐面子而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.79,0:14:19.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那小佐和要不要一起去？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.92,0:14:23.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次去海外是和學生們一起嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.06,0:14:25.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.31,0:14:28.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就度蜜月的時候去吧  小佐和
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.94,0:14:32.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真棒啊  蜜月～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.13,0:14:34.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要拍咯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.24,0:14:40.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  全部湊齊  這就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.63,0:14:44.50,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（護照申請辦理處）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.26,0:14:50.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.32,0:14:54.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紬紬  謝謝你陪我們過來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.64,0:14:55.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.49,0:14:58.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家東西都帶齊了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.43,0:14:58.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.01,0:14:59.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.87,0:15:01.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,律你也帶齊了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.45,0:15:02.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.56,0:15:03.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.37,0:15:12.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.16,0:15:16.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…學生手冊忘帶了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.17,0:15:18.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去拿嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.55,0:15:20.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用  叫聰送來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.67,0:15:24.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  聰  現在有空嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.37,0:15:30.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好熱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.61,0:15:31.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.38,0:15:35.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊有發團扇的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.55,0:15:36.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.70,0:15:40.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說…也用不著到外邊來等吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.26,0:15:44.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想吃冰淇淋…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.94,0:15:47.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辦完再說啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.17,0:15:50.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.47,0:15:51.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.17,0:15:52.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.20,0:15:56.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐真是的  下次注意點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.74,0:15:57.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.07,0:16:01.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  小澪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.32,0:16:01.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.23,0:16:04.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小律的弟弟是個怎麼樣的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.31,0:16:09.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個啊…有點像小律吧  特別是眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.65,0:16:11.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  小律男生版
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.86,0:16:14.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弟弟啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.93,0:16:19.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐真是的  下次注意點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.59,0:16:21.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  感覺不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.60,0:16:24.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有個弟弟確實挺不錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.21,0:16:26.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「姐姐真是的  下次注意點啊」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.99,0:16:29.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  要是唯學姐當弟弟的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.76,0:16:30.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.10,0:16:32.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.24,0:16:33.74,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}發證窗口
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.24,0:16:33.74,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}填好申請書後，準備好申請文件排隊辦理
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.24,0:16:33.74,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}照片由工作人員黏貼，請在窗口與申請書共同提交
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.15,0:16:39.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於能提交了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.61,0:16:43.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是秋山同學先吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.10,0:16:45.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按學號來？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.03,0:16:47.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  下一位
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.65,0:16:50.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩您了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.51,0:16:55.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  這張照片不能用
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.70,0:16:56.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.50,0:16:59.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡必須要留有空白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.56,0:17:04.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為不知道上面有什麼隱藏的東西  所以不能用
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.90,0:17:09.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼把頭髮紮起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.59,0:17:12.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為覺得看起來會成熟一點…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.48,0:17:16.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為日本人到了國外看起來比較像小孩子的關係吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.48,0:17:20.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓喵這樣的就跟小學生差不多？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.73,0:17:22.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯學姐不也是一樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.45,0:17:23.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.86,0:17:26.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係  重新照一張就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.52,0:17:29.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊有能拍證件照的機器
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.60,0:17:32.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我昨天用過  絕對沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.84,0:17:39.65,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎使用
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.84,0:17:40.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把簾子拉上咯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.44,0:17:43.16,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請在畫面上選擇所需要的服務
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.14,0:17:49.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到會在證件照上出問題
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.26,0:17:51.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辦個護照也不容易啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.64,0:17:56.25,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請做好準備後按下照相鍵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.98,0:17:55.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因為不容易才會更有喜悅感吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.49,0:17:58.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直很佩服你樂觀向上的精神
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.00,0:17:58.80,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拍照會進行兩次
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.44,0:18:00.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辦好之後去吃冰淇淋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.17,0:18:02.63,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼開始拍攝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.30,0:18:04.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有那些東西就沒有動力這點  我可不敢苟同
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.18,0:18:05.69,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3 2 1
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.69,0:18:09.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都害我笑出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.71,0:18:10.34,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始第二次拍攝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.38,0:18:11.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑容有什麼不好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.16,0:18:13.63,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3 2 1
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.68,0:18:14.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用作護照的照片可能不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.05,0:18:17.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要重拍了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.24,0:18:20.07,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拍照會進行兩次
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.52,0:18:24.99,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼開始拍攝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.71,0:18:28.23,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3 2 1
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.80,0:18:28.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.54,0:18:33.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得裡面會很熱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.54,0:18:34.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.57,0:18:39.58,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始第二次拍攝  3 2 1
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.81,0:18:37.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,律！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.54,0:18:38.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼會知道是我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.81,0:18:39.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.90,0:18:44.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真是的  又成這樣了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.89,0:18:49.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於結束了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.47,0:18:51.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是累死了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.06,0:18:53.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這都怪誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.34,0:18:54.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.51,0:18:58.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過正因如此  冰淇淋變得好吃極了～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.46,0:19:01.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你對甜食還真是樂觀向上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.28,0:19:02.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.60,0:19:06.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,證件照到底拍了多少次啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.09,0:19:07.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.10,0:19:11.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且這要怎麼處理…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.73,0:19:13.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留作紀念
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.61,0:19:19.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.96,0:19:22.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.91,0:19:35.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過一星期左右還要再過來拿護照呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.81,0:19:37.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等夏季講習結束了再去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.00,0:19:41.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有我們到底準備去哪裡旅行…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.12,0:19:42.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也得決定下來…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.85,0:19:44.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪兒好呢～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.11,0:19:46.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去英國看演唱會
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.64,0:19:47.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏威夷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.55,0:19:48.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美國
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.60,0:19:50.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泡溫泉打乒乓球如何
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.31,0:19:52.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就不用來辦護照了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.32,0:19:53.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.05,0:19:57.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就去兩次畢業旅行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.87,0:20:01.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等到梓喵畢業的時候也去就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.82,0:20:03.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我畢業的時候也是大家一起去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.96,0:20:04.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.98,0:20:10.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話  英國  夏威夷  美國  溫泉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.64,0:20:12.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都能去一遍咯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.58,0:20:18.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們哪裡都可以去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.42,0:20:21.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.40,0:20:27.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.27,0:20:31.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  去看看海外旅行所需要的東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.57,0:20:33.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.21,0:20:34.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出發出發
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.12,0:20:39.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  充滿海外旅行的味道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.61,0:20:40.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小律  小律
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.99,0:20:41.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.20,0:20:45.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了它的話  上課時候也能大睡特睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.37,0:20:46.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.54,0:20:48.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,律需要這些吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.61,0:20:50.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身為日本人必不可少
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.88,0:20:52.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No rice, No life
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.08,0:20:55.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也需要嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.38,0:21:00.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是錢被偷了  我們就在街頭賣唱賺錢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.59,0:21:02.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  海外出道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.65,0:21:07.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We are 「放學後茶會」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.72,0:21:08.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…好長
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.77,0:21:10.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡稱「HTT」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.90,0:21:14.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,英語的話  不是應該是「After School Teatime」嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.00,0:21:18.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不管到哪裡都是「放學後茶會」哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.59,0:21:24.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過旅行不能帶上樂器吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.82,0:21:27.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空氣吉他  這是空氣吉他
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.58,0:21:30.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Believe的人就能看見！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.65,0:21:32.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那奇怪的說話方式還是省省吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.90,0:21:35.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這肯定無論到哪兒都改不了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.75,0:21:40.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  護照到手～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.30,0:21:42.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.16,0:21:43.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰都能弄到的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.91,0:21:47.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然比我先去海外…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.59,0:21:50.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以小佐和也一起去嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.06,0:21:52.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等到蜜月的時候會去的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.12,0:21:54.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說來…我們要去哪裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.50,0:21:56.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等到畢業的時候再說唄
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.83,0:21:58.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在還是夏天嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.33,0:22:01.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前還有夏季講習吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.65,0:22:04.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No  夏季講習…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.69,0:22:06.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會好好用功的啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.74,0:22:07.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
